<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 21:23:57 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4c1ceb1805f</link><description>&lt;p&gt;来自格雷森高地的照片拼贴——小马和露营地&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Photo collage from Grayson Highlands - ponies and campsite" height="1024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chrisod/6a4c1ceb1805f.jpg" width="1024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chrisod.some.pics"&gt;@chrisod&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 21:23:57 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>格雷森高地山景</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4c1a5105b9b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;格雷森高地州立公园的山景&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Mountain view from Grayson Highlands State Park" height="1456" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/chrisod/6a4c1a5105b9b.jpg" width="3248"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://chrisod.some.pics"&gt;@chrisod&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 21:12:52 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>内外</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4bcd4258189</link><description>&lt;p&gt;内部外部。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Rain, a car rearview mirror, facade of a house." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a4bcd4258189.jpg" width="1125"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 15:44:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4b7feecf71b</link><description>&lt;p&gt;粉色与蓝绿色&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The interior of a typical Norwegian wooden church from the 1830s, featuring doors in front of the pews, a two-storey gallery and a pulpit-altar (a characteristic Norwegian feature from the 19th century). The wooden walls and columns are painted teal, whilst the panelling and the walls of the two galleries are painted in a pink marble-effect finish. The columns in the nave and around the pulpit altar are also painted in a marble-effect finish (those around the altar in pink). A pale pink carpet runs from the entrance to the altar. A brass-coloured chandelier hangs from the ceiling. The church is one of the largest in the region and has a total of 700 seats … just to put that into perspective when compared with churches in other countries. " height="3648" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a4b7feecf71b.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 10:14:13 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>电量满格</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4ae42fc5ecf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;低电量转满电量&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A small black and white dog stretches out on her stomach in the sun, in a scrubby patch of grass and weeds. She’s staring at the ground like she’s dazed." height="2448" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jinx/6a4ae42fc5ecf.jpg" width="3264"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jinx.some.pics"&gt;@jinx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 23:09:39 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>